<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[deep fry chicken / tofu, potatoes, and shallots separately, pat dry]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[put the chicken / tofu in a pan and just cover with coconut milk, and bring to boil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add cardamom pods, peanuts, bay leaves, 10 mins]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the potatoes an onions]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[in another pot cook coconut cream and curry paste, low heat, 10 m. use juice from (4) if it gets too dry]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[when dry, add sugar until caramelized]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add fish sauce and tamarind water]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add (7)  to (4), add the pinea[[le / apple juice, and serve]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
